  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of the present study is to develop a prognostic tool to assess the risk of dead and
      major complications in patient admitted to hospital for infection. A detailed database of
      clinical, biochemical and microbiological data is recorded and each item is analyzed and
      compared with clinical outcomes to develop a prognostic score.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
